published>2023-10-27T10:09:44-04:00</published><updated> 2023-10-27T10:09:44-04:00</updated><title>由于特斯拉不断受损，赫兹正在缩减其电动汽车雄心</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;赫兹客户测试电动汽车&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/xYnn-e_d7jn5PLE3Z-CiucJbdnQ=/77x0:2923x1897/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn. com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72799994/1556855574.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：Rodin Eckenroth / Getty Images for Hertz&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;w9fHxh&quot;>;赫兹曾经设想的租车公司作为最终的电动汽车经纪人，该公司向商务旅客、网约车司机和技术新手发放电池驱动的汽车，这是一项雄心勃勃的计划，旨在推动电动汽车革命。该公司与特斯拉和 Polestar 签署了购买近 20 万辆电动汽车的协议。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2021/10/25/22744504/hertz-tesla-order-100000-vehicles-electrify-fleet&quot;>;消息传出后，特斯拉估值突破 1 万亿美元&lt;/a>; .&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;9uATcE&quot;>;但与电动汽车开关的许多其他方面一样，该计划也遇到了一些阻力。赫兹本周表示，由于其电动汽车的转售价值直线下降以及维修成本高昂，该公司正在暂停其电动汽车的推出。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;Gdr1e3&quot;>;特斯拉一直在大幅降价以刺激销售，因为它发现自己正在努力应对需求疲软和竞争加剧的问题。维修费用约为两倍...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/27/23934691/hertz-tesla-uber-ev-plans-damage -repair-price-cuts&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/27/23934691/hertz-tesla-uber-ev-plans-damage-repair-price-cuts" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/27/23934691/hertz-tesla-uber-ev-plans-damage-repair-price-cuts</id><author><name>安德鲁·霍金斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-10-27T10:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2023-10-27T10:00:00-04:00</updated><title>埃隆·马斯克的 Twitter，一年后</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;被谴责的鸟舍的照片插图，上面覆盖着涂鸦和警示胶带。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Gf66qgJnBIn6w5ZGDTrv5Ts8Rhw=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72799915/236862_YTD_Twitter_FINAL_CVirginia.0 .jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;照片插图由 Cath Virginia / The Verge 提供 |照片由 Getty Images 提供&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;这是个人恩怨、轻率的品牌重塑和令人震惊的政策转变的一年。这些甚至还不是最糟糕的部分。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23934205/elon-musk-twitter-x-one-year-later-acquisition&quot; >;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23934205/elon-musk-twitter-x-one-year-later-acquisition" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23934205/elon-musk-twitter-x-one-year-later-acquisition</id><author><name>杰·彼得斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-10-27T09:30:00-04:00</published><updated> 2023-10-27T09:30:00-04:00</updated><title>在《心灵杀手 2》中，你永远不会感到安全</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;《心灵杀手 2》的屏幕截图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/dQ8xYKNnSlE2QYNeWtXbfq6Lqq8=/600x0:3840x2160/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72799836/AW2_10_08_23_002.0 .png&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Remedy Entertainment&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;Remedy Entertainment 在十多年后重返该系列，带来既奇怪又可怕的生存恐怖体验。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt; a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23934662/alan-wake-2-review-ps5-xbox-pc&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23934662/alan-wake-2-review-ps5-xbox-pc" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23934662/alan-wake-2-review-ps5-xbox-pc</id><author><name>陶里克·穆萨</name></author></entry></feed>